// The core insight: Signals work because they're COSTLY
// A signal that anyone can fake is worthless
// A signal that only capable people can produce is valuable

print "THE SPENCE SIGNALING MODEL";
print "──────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────";
print "";
print "A signal is valuable when:";
print "  1. It's COSTLY to produce (time, effort, skill)";
